Most people who =E2=80=9Ccollaborate=E2=80=9D on a piece don=E2=80=99t do i=
t intentionally or synchronously. They are intentional creators of their ow=
n piece, and unwitting collaborators on future ones. This unwitting collabo=
ration plays out over weeks, months, years, or decades. Someone contributes=
