erson to try it. <strong>The proceeds from the sale will be split with the =
26 people whose work I referenced and the people who share it</strong> (if =
I have their ETH address; the unclaimed amounts will go to charity).</p><p =
style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1e=
