in will take home the most, with 8%, because her writing on the Passion Eco=
nomy was fundamental to the piece.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1=
a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">You can bid on t=
